00:34:17.259 --> 00:34:19.005
I’d never know that…

00:34:20.688 --> 00:34:22.339
you’re this cute.

00:34:30.833 --> 00:34:33.788
So what happens to you and me
ten years from now?

00:34:34.042 --> 00:34:35.053
Tell me already.

00:34:36.169 --> 00:34:37.118
We’re boyfriends.

00:34:49.760 --> 00:34:52.390
Gosh, I’m freaking sleepy.

00:34:53.150 --> 00:34:55.208
Class hasn’t even started yet,
and you’re already sleepy?

00:34:55.578 --> 00:34:57.448
I just hate morning classes.

00:34:58.003 --> 00:34:58.592
Hey.

00:34:59.537 --> 00:35:00.415
You’re fully recovered?

00:35:00.964 --> 00:35:02.142
I’m better now.

00:35:02.635 --> 00:35:04.149
Hey, your cast is off.

00:35:04.416 --> 00:35:05.726
Does it mean you can go home?

00:35:16.407 --> 00:35:17.052
Farm.

00:35:17.812 --> 00:35:18.312
Yeah?

00:35:18.887 --> 00:35:20.431
Will you go to the bathroom with me?

00:35:26.696 --> 00:35:27.938
I’m coming too.

00:35:27.938 --> 00:35:28.438
Hey,

00:35:28.952 --> 00:35:31.190
if we don’t get back
before roll call, cover for us.

00:35:33.244 --> 00:35:34.780
Yeah, sure.

00:35:37.368 --> 00:35:38.514
Hey, Jinn.

00:35:39.212 --> 00:35:40.600
Will you come sit next to me?

00:35:42.284 --> 00:35:43.659
I’m literally right in front of you.

00:35:43.659 --> 00:35:44.775
Why would I move next to you?

00:35:46.418 --> 00:35:48.816
I just want someone beside me.

00:35:48.816 --> 00:35:49.819
Oh, yeah?

00:35:49.819 --> 00:35:51.513
Someone beside you?

00:35:52.684 --> 00:35:53.709
Go sit with your dad.

00:36:00.959 --> 00:36:01.670
What’s wrong?

00:36:08.049 --> 00:36:09.050
