from the notebook, I realized…

00:45:10.579 --> 00:45:12.086
how much I’d been overlooking.

00:45:16.214 --> 00:45:18.910
So what happens to you and me
ten years from now?

00:45:20.471 --> 00:45:21.573
Tell me already.

00:45:25.085 --> 00:45:25.977
We’re boyfriends.

00:45:26.573 --> 00:45:27.178
