00:46:31.629 --> 00:46:33.307
So, what do we do now?

00:46:33.800 --> 00:46:34.806
What the heck are we waiting for?

00:46:35.073 --> 00:46:35.997
We’re boyfriends, of course.

00:46:37.394 --> 00:46:38.521
I can’t sleep.

00:46:38.644 --> 00:46:40.548
I want to cuddle my boyfriend.

00:46:41.061 --> 00:46:42.742
I’m gonna put this on the table, Mom.

00:46:42.742 --> 00:46:43.258
Sure.

00:46:46.688 --> 00:46:48.151
How long are you going to keep doing this?

00:46:48.284 --> 00:46:51.387
Until someone comes along to
take care of you in my place, I guess.

00:46:52.126 --> 00:46:53.710
Don’t you want to take care of me forever?

00:46:54.696 --> 00:46:58.497
What if everything that’s happened
is just a coincidence?

00:46:58.579 --> 00:47:03.284
Well, at least my feelings turned out real.